column1: # DAY 1 SPRINT RESULTS: STRATIFIED K-FOLD CV + BOOTSTRAP CIs
# AUC: Area Under ROC Curve (0.5 = random
# PR_AUC: Area Under Precision-Recall Curve (better for imbalanced data)
# Brier_Score: Mean squared error of probability predictions (0 = perfect
# Precision: True Positives / (True Positives + False Positives)
# Recall: True Positives / (True Positives + False Negatives)
# F1_Score: Harmonic mean of precision and recall
# Bootstrap_CI: 95% confidence interval from 1000 bootstrap resamples
# Statistical_Testing: DeLong tests and paired bootstrap tests pending for Day 2
# Statistical testing pending - DeLong tests scheduled for Day 2
# Bootstrap CIs: 95% confidence intervals from 1000 resamples
